To use tripwire to protect your systems, you should first initialise
the databases:

	(cd ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}; ${PREFIX}/sbin/tripwire -initialize)

which creates the database in the ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/databases
directory.

===========================================================================
